item.title: 2015 Chromebook Pixel
item.description: I just got a Chromebook pixel today and it is gorgeous. It embodies simplicity and minimalism while still being completely functional. Unboxing it was a great experience. When you take it out and open it up for the first time, it turns on in an instant and it is ready for you to pick a WiFi connection and log in. I canâ€™t remember using a computer so responsive to my input, it feels really fast.
